The paper discusses practical challenges and lessons learned from applying deep learning to real-world tasks, which suggests that it belongs to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The specific case studies mentioned in the abstract also suggest that it may belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and software engineering (cs.SE) sub-categories.
